:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534309\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ywq1665702746300.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ywq1665702746300.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ywq1665702746300.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ywq1665702746300\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n Return Sentinel Licenses for the Community Edition\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If you want to install the Uniface Community Edition on a different machine, you have\n      to return the license from your existing machine.</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__context_w945ab1b5b1_w946ab1b5_w947ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__p_d65402e1_d65403e1_d65404e1\">You will need to have the Entitlement ID from the email that you received when you registered to download Uniface.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__p_d65405e1_d65406e1_d65407e1\">To return a license:</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__li_d28388e1_d28389e1_d28390e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__p_d65408e1_d65409e1_d65410e1\">Start the License Return utility from the Start\n               menu.  </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\"><img alt=\"License Return Utility Wizard\" class=\"image\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__image_ktq_2w4_tvb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/celau_returnlicense.png?_LANG=enus\"/></div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__li_d28391e1_d28392e1_d28393e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"ywq1665702746300__p_d65411e1_d65412e1_d65413e1\">Copy your Entitlement ID and paste it into the\n               form, then press <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Return License</span>. This returns the license to\n               the Sentinel Cloud Server and removes the license configuration file from this\n               machine. You will not be able to run Uniface again without activating the license. To\n               reactivate a license, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pmh1665702746374.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pmh1665702746374.html\" title=\"The License Activation utility is responsible for activating and downloading Sentinel cloud-served licenses. Uniface licenses for the Community Edition are managed by the Sentinel Cloud Server. Uniface connects to Sentinel to check out licenses and renew the lease on licenses on a regular basis.\">Activate Sentinel Licenses for the Community Edition</a>. </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534309\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534309\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Return Sentinel Licenses for the Community Edition Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return Sentinel Licenses for the Community Edition If you want to install the Uniface Community Edition on a different machine, you have to return the license from your existing machine. You will need to have the Entitlement ID from the email that you received when you registered to download Uniface. To return a license: Start the License Return utility from the Start menu. Copy your Entitlement ID and paste it into the form, then press Return License . This returns the license to the Sentinel Cloud Server and removes the license configuration file from this machine. You will not be able to run Uniface again without activating the license. To reactivate a license, see Activate Sentinel Licenses for the Community Edition . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}